BCM Agent for Kubernetes
Copyright 2025 Fabien Dupont <fdupont@redhat.com>

This project contains Kubernetes/OpenShift integration code for NVIDIA Base
Command Manager (BCM). The integration code (src/, helm/, kubernetes/, docs/,
scripts/) is licensed under the Apache License 2.0 (see LICENSE file).

===============================================================================

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES

This software requires NVIDIA's proprietary cm-lite-daemon, which is NOT
included in this repository and must be obtained separately from your NVIDIA
Base Command Manager installation.

