Any use, reproduction, disclosure or distribution of cm-lite-daemon and related
documentation requires an express license agreement from NVIDIA CORPORATION.

The cm-lite-daemon must be obtained from your NVIDIA Base Command Manager
installation, typically located at:
  /cm/shared/apps/cm-lite-daemon-dist/cm-lite-daemon.zip

For licensing questions regarding cm-lite-daemon, contact NVIDIA Corporation.

===============================================================================

BUILD REQUIREMENTS

To build container images using this project, you must:

1. Have a valid NVIDIA Base Command Manager installation
2. Have access to the cm-lite-daemon distribution
3. Copy cm-lite-daemon.zip to the build context before building
4. Build the container image on a system with access to BCM files
5. NOT redistribute the resulting container image publicly

The container image built from this project contains NVIDIA proprietary
software and is subject to NVIDIA's licensing terms.

===============================================================================

